<plot>This documentary treats movie fans to a behind-the-scenes look at the making of Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles, the live-action film adaptation of the popular comic book and animated series. Included are interviews with the cast and crew who share their experiences from making the film, as well as disscuss the efforts that went into it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?574103</url></doc>
